title: The North American Waste-to-Energy Conference Call for Proposals is OPEN (Energy Recovery Council)
text: ( Source : Energy Recovery Council ) The NAWTEC 2016 Call for Proposals is Now Open and the deadline is November 16 , 2015 . NAWTEC 24 will take place in West Palm Beach, Florida , on May 23-25, 2016. The North American Waste-to-Energy Conference
